  <summary date="2021-09-30T16:06:52Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Fair Sugar Policy Act of 2019

This bill makes several modifications to the Department of Agriculture's sugar program. Among other modifications, the bill decreases the rate for price support loans, repeals the marketing allotments, revises the administration of import quotas, and repeals the Feedstock Flexibility Program.</summary>
